---
const founders = [
  {
    initial: 'A',
    name: 'Alex',
    role: 'Operations & Strategy',
  },
  {
    initial: 'A',
    name: 'Ana',
    role: 'Systems & Implementation',
  },
];
---

<section class="py-24 px-6 bg-brand-bg">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-start">

      <!-- Left: Authority text -->
      <div>
        <p class="section-label mb-6">Why Retiply</p>
        <h2 class="font-poppins font-bold text-3xl md:text-5xl text-brand-text leading-tight mb-8">
          We know what<br class="hidden md:block" />
          actually works.
        </h2>
        <div class="space-y-5 font-inter text-base text-brand-muted leading-relaxed mb-10">
          <p>
            Thirty years of operational experience across project-based businesses.
            We have run the numbers, felt the pressure, made the hard calls.
            That is not a background. That is our specific knowledge position.
          </p>
          <p>
            And now we work on the frontier of AI: not in theory, not in a demo
            environment, but in real businesses with real people. We understand
            what the technology can actually do today, and more importantly,
            how people adopt it. Human psychology. Change management. What
            actually sticks versus what sounds good in a pitch.
          </p>
          <p>
            That combination, deep operational knowledge and up-to-date technical
            expertise, is what makes Retiply different from every other automation
            agency you will talk to.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Pull quote -->
        <blockquote class="border-l-2 border-brand-accent pl-6">
          <p class="font-poppins font-medium text-lg md:text-xl text-brand-text leading-snug">
            "We have run businesses like yours. We know what is breaking it.
            And we know how to fix it."
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>

      <!-- Right: Founder cards -->
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-5 lg:pt-16">
        {founders.map((founder) => (
          <div class="bg-brand-surface rounded-2xl p-7 flex items-center gap-6">
            <!-- Avatar placeholder -->
            <div
              class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-brand-accent flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0"
            >
              <span class="font-poppins font-semibold text-xl text-white">
                {founder.initial}
              </span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="font-poppins font-semibold text-lg text-brand-text mb-1">
                {founder.name}
              </p>
              <p class="font-inter text-sm text-brand-muted">
                {founder.role}
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}

        <!-- Stat block -->
        <div class="bg-brand-surface rounded-2xl p-7 mt-2">
          <p class="font-poppins font-bold text-4xl text-brand-accent mb-2">30+</p>
          <p class="font-inter text-sm text-brand-muted leading-relaxed">
            Years of combined operational experience across project-based
            businesses, now applied through AI.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
